'Greetings, [placeholder].

'An evil plagues the lands of Umbar and Ikorbân and we cannot allow it to spread.

'I ask that you gather your allies and travel to The Depths of Mâkhda Khorbo and The Temple of Utug-bûr and defeat the evils who lurk in their halls. Do this, and I can provide you with a reward to match your efforts.'
Return to the Temple of Utug-bûr Quartermaster with proof of your victory.
'I have heard of your deeds in The Depths of Mâkhda Khorbo and The Temple of Utug-bûr.\n\n'Please accept this as a token of my thanks to you and your companions.'
